               <p>I live in Foster-lane, Cheapside; I am a cheesemonger, wholesale and retail; I have known Flaxman near two years; he as draft with me nearly that time; he keeps a small chandler's shop.</p>
               <p>Q. During the time you have known him, what is his character? - A. He bore a general good charecter, as far as I have heard of him.</p>
