               <p>I live in Oxford-street: I am in the oil and colour way; I have known Flaxman between two and three years; I never heard any thing bad of him in my life; he deals with me, I serve him with any credit that is reasonable for his situation.</p>
               <p>Mr. Knowlys. I have a vast number of witnesses to his character, but I will not trouble the Court with any more.</p>

